Introduction

Rui (루이) is a Japanese rapper under New Planet Entertainment. She is the leader and visual of the girl group H.U.B. She is also a former member of the pre-debut girl group N-Bulance. Prior to H.U.B, she debuted as a soloist on August 17, 2016 with the single "Exciting".
